				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote8-12455_000_023"><a name="8-12455_000_023"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote8-12455_000_023">8.</a></span>
					<p>Thomas S. Monson, “The Will Within,” <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> May 1987, 68.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote9-12455_000_023"><a name="9-12455_000_023"> </a>
